com.clxcommunications.xms.api

Class MtBatchDryRunResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.clxcommunications.xms.api.MtBatchDryRunResult

  • @Value.Immutable
public abstract class MtBatchDryRunResult
extends Object
    The result of a message batch dry-run. The XMS API allows users to simulate sending batches and this result class contains information that allow you to analyze various aspects of a batch run before it is actually performed.

    It is, for example possible to see how many actual SMS messages will be sent as part of the batch.
